    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/4a162e21339d70b6d05ca92515eeec08.poster.avif?t=1758679792\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/4a162e21339d70b6d05ca92515eeec08.webm?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/4a162e21339d70b6d05ca92515eeec08.mp4?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MachineClad is a mech customization action game where you assemble your own machine from body and weapon parts to take on missions and arena battles.Use Boost Dash to outmaneuver enemies with instantaneous mobility, lock onto them with your Lock-on circle, and open fire. Experience the exhilarating combat only mechs can offer.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The combat unit &quot;MachineClad&quot; that the player pilots is made up of nine parts: five body parts, four weapon slots, and optional chips. Lock-on distance and radius, turning performance, defense—all depend on how you build your mech.Customize your build to suit the mission and enemy you're facing to gain the upper hand—or stick to your favorite tactics and loadout to power through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/90319b6dc3fc211dd309a0c3fb409662.poster.avif?t=1758679792\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/90319b6dc3fc211dd309a0c3fb409662.webm?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/90319b6dc3fc211dd309a0c3fb409662.mp4?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MISSION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an independent mercenary, you'll take on combat missions from various factions in exchange for rewards. Missions range from enemy elimination and base defense to exploration—and sometimes even battles against massive bosses. Use your earnings to upgrade and customize your build, and complete missions efficiently to raise your reputation as a top-tier mercenary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/a41ac54ec7f763175701a984af322dbf.poster.avif?t=1758679792\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/a41ac54ec7f763175701a984af322dbf.webm?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/a41ac54ec7f763175701a984af322dbf.mp4?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARENA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dedicated mode for battling other mercenaries—known as &quot;Clads&quot;—who pilot their own MachineClads. Each opponent in the Arena showcases unique tactics, making them ideal challengers to test your skills. Their distinctive bios also offer glimpses into the world and its lore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/4ef0d5c92a10e0bfdd434b904f53a8c8.poster.avif?t=1758679792\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/4ef0d5c92a10e0bfdd434b904f53a8c8.webm?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297860/extras/4ef0d5c92a10e0bfdd434b904f53a8c8.mp4?t=1758679792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
